{"tid":1492763,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「戰略」 唔想輸麻煩入黎睇睇","createTime":"2019-08-21T03:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T03:34:40.000Z","uid":184099,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"001cc79e10e0a35dc7d6216024fd30e51924a017","tid":1492763,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"某垃圾大學 社會心理學畢業<br />\n <br />\n近日twitter同fb都已經做緊中共假信息清理，<br />\n就知假信息既重要性。<br />\n場運動好大機會輸起《信息戰》。<br />\n唔想輸睇埋落去<br />\n <br />\n懶人包總結：<br />\n中國紅媒將《將軍澳斬人》報道為：暴徒自編自導自演。<br />\n《平反64紅衣》報道為：上海人被暴徒毆打，澄清是P圖。<br />\n <br />\n中國實行緊愚民政策，<br />\n掌控媒體同信息渠道黎洗腦。<br />\n每年花費最多精力既就係清理《假海報》<br />\n你地就知呢D《假海報》對中國黎講威脅幾咁大。<br />\n <br />\n《假信息戰已展開》，不需大量澄清，只需要作出大量反擊。因為信息戰攻擊成本低，但澄清成本高。<br />\n<br />\n例如：成立獨立調查委員會，還警察一個公道<br />\n例如：號召天安門集會，支持香港警察<br />\n例如：宣傳中國是民主自由國家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZsXCcO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZsXCcO.png&h=7ed386dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5G13SP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5G13SP.png&h=255c548a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSTPtju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSTPtju.png&h=7e9fb831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n唔好睇少呢D手段，<br />\n14億人，得1%人信，已經1400萬人口<br />\n信息真假已經唔重要，重要既係立場清晰。<br />\n <br />\n《假信息》只合適中國内地，<br />\n海外地區需要進行《標簽化》，例如近期既：Chinazi等等。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n軟戰爭已響起號角，大家準備好味？反擊味？"},{"pid":"204de85b36d4897f3d5d341a4f459e44dbff1e68","tid":1492763,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"603fc09214da07dcba18ab64b6a380ad3459db17","tid":1492763,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:33:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"529117857f8ed95e4ae73009c54a81da98f67e8e","tid":1492763,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"16374ab7b21a843e0ff03a558c26e8674870bb4e","tid":1492763,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:34:40.000Z","msg":"你想講嘅戰略係?"}]}